From: "Xin Li (Intel)" <xin@zytor.com>
Date: Sun, 27 Apr 2025 02:20:16 -0700
Subject: x86/msr: Rename rdpmcl() to rdpmc()
Git-commit: 7d9ccde56bc023f9a968db537963a029aa41d902
Patch-mainline: v6.16-rc1
References: jsc#PED-15480

Now that rdpmc() is gone, rdpmcl() is the sole PMC read helper,
simply rename rdpmcl() to rdpmc().

